<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify Your MedicalHub Account</title>
</head>

<body
    style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
    <header style="background-color: #0077be; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
        <h1 style="margin: 0;">MedicalHub Platform</h1>
    </header>
    <main style="padding: 20px;">
        <h2 style="color: #0077be;">Verify Your Email Address</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Hello,</p>
        <p>To complete your account setup and ensure the security of your account, please verify your email address by
            clicking the button below:</p>
        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <a href="<%= verification_link %>"
                style="display: inline-block; background-color: #0077be; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold;">Verify
                My Email</a>
        </div>
        <p>If the button above doesn't work, you can also copy and paste the following link into your browser:</p>
        <p style="word-break: break-all; background-color: #f0f0f0; padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px;">
            <%= verification_link %>
        </p>
        <p><strong>Important:</strong> This link will expire in 30 minutes for security reasons.</p>
        <div style="background-color: #f9f9f9; border-left: 4px solid #0077be; padding: 15px; margin-top: 20px;">
            <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Note:</strong> For your security, please do not share this email or the
                verification link with anyone.</p>
        </div>
    </main>
    <footer style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; font-size: 0.8em; color: #666;">
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact our support team at
            support@MedicalHubplatform.com
        </p>
        <p>&copy; 2024 MedicalHub Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>